Wireframe Text for Chit Fund Application
1. User Registration / Login Page
Header:

Title: "Welcome to [Platform Name]"
Subtitle: "Join or Login to your Account"
Registration Form:

Input Field: Name
Input Field: Email
Input Field: Phone
Input Field: Password
Button: "Register"
Login Form (if user chooses to login):

Input Field: Email
Input Field: Password
Button: "Login"
Footer:

Links: "Terms of Service", "Privacy Policy"
2. Dashboard (After Login)
Navbar:

Logo (top left)
Links: Home | Groups | User Profile | About | Contact | Logout (top right)
Hero Section:

Title: "Welcome, [User Name]"
Brief description of userâ€™s role (e.g., "Chit Creator" or "Participant")
Button: "Create a Chit Fund" (if Chit Creator)
My Chit Funds Section:

Header: "My Active Chit Funds"
List of Chit Funds:
Card for each Chit Fund
Chit Fund Name
Total Amount
Duration
Button: "View Details"
Available Chit Funds Section:

Header: "Available Chit Funds"
List of Chit Funds:
Card for each Chit Fund
Chit Fund Name
Description
Button: "Join Fund"
3. Chit Fund Creation Page (for Chit Creators)
Header:

Title: "Create a New Chit Fund"
Form Fields:

Input Field: Chit Fund Name
Input Field: Total Amount
Input Field: Duration (in months)
Input Field: Start Date
Input Field: End Date
Button: "Create Chit Fund"
4. Chit Fund Details Page
Header:

Title: "[Chit Fund Name] Details"
Information Section:

Total Amount: [Amount]
Duration: [Duration]
Start Date: [Start Date]
End Date: [End Date]
Participants List: [List of Participants]
Action Buttons:

Button: "Make Contribution"
Button: "Place Bid" (if applicable)
5. User Profile Page
Header:

Title: "User Profile"
Profile Information:

Label: Name: [User Name]
Label: Email: [User Email]
Label: Phone: [User Phone]
Button: "Edit Profile"
KYC Documents Section:

Label: KYC Status: [Verified/Not Verified]
Button: "Upload KYC Documents"
6. Notifications Page
Header:

Title: "Notifications"
Notification List:

List of Notifications:
Notification Message: [Message]
